@startuml sequence_chat_lifecycle
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Chat Widget Lifecycle (L2-020)

actor Visitor
participant "ChatWidget\n(collapsed FAB)" as FAB
participant "ChatContainer\nuseChat hook" as Container
participant "POST\n/conversations" as ConvoAPI
participant "POST\n/conversations/{id}/messages" as MsgAPI
database "chat.*" as DB

== Open Widget ==
Visitor -> FAB: Click chat icon
FAB -> FAB: setIsOpen(true)
FAB --> Visitor: Expanded chat card\n"How can we help?"

== First Message ==
Visitor -> FAB: Type message & submit
FAB -> Container: onSubmit(message)
Container -> ConvoAPI: POST /api/chat/conversations
ConvoAPI -> DB: INSERT conversation
DB --> ConvoAPI: { id }
ConvoAPI --> Container: 201 { id }
Container -> Container: Store conversationId\nin sessionStorage

== Streaming Exchange ==
Container -> MsgAPI: POST { messages }\nvia useChat
MsgAPI -> DB: INSERT user message
MsgAPI --> Container: Stream tokens...
Container --> FAB: Render tokens\nincrementally
note right: AI response appears\nword by word
MsgAPI -> DB: INSERT assistant message\n(onFinish callback)

== Continue or Close ==
Visitor -> FAB: Send another message
FAB -> Container: onSubmit(message)
Container -> MsgAPI: POST { messages }\n(same conversationId)
note right: Full conversation\nhistory sent for context

Visitor -> FAB: Click X to close
FAB -> FAB: setIsOpen(false)
FAB --> Visitor: Collapsed FAB icon

@enduml
